Two pills at a time.

00:19:46.119 --> 00:19:47.079
Ouch, ouch, ouch.

00:19:50.039 --> 00:19:50.599
Ouch, ouch, ouch.

00:19:50.599 --> 00:19:51.960
Be gentle.

