Is the injury any better?

00:21:40.680 --> 00:21:41.359
No.

00:21:46.559 --> 00:21:47.079
Ouch.

00:21:47.680 --> 00:21:48.880
Oh, oh, oh.

00:21:50.039 --> 00:21:50.880
Keep acting.

