00:22:18.400 --> 00:22:19.480
Who could it be?

00:22:19.839 --> 00:22:20.880
Oshima Hiroshi?

00:22:21.200 --> 00:22:22.319
Besides Oshima Hiroshi,

00:22:22.920 --> 00:22:24.240
who we should be more wary of

00:22:24.559 --> 00:22:26.480
is another pair of unseen eyes.

00:22:31.480 --> 00:22:32.839
Is there any solution?

00:22:33.680 --> 00:22:35.000
I do have a plan,

00:22:35.279 --> 00:22:36.960
but it requires your cooperation.

00:22:37.119 --> 00:22:38.480
No problem, tell me.

00:22:43.480 --> 00:22:44.640
Move in with me.

00:23:38.079 --> 00:23:39.039
Where did you go?

00:23:41.200 --> 00:23:42.039
What are you doing?

00:23:42.599 --> 00:23:43.480
I'm sorry.

00:23:43.680 --> 00:23:44.319
Go away.

00:24:30.200 --> 00:24:32.200
Jimmy, I'm coming.

00:25:36.240 --> 00:25:37.119
Witt.

00:25:37.480 --> 00:25:38.480
Witt.

00:25:40.920 --> 00:25:41.720
What's wrong?

00:25:42.200 --> 00:25:43.680
Are you feeling unwell somewhere?

00:25:46.759 --> 00:25:47.480
I'm fine.

00:25:48.519 --> 00:25:49.200
I'm fine.

00:25:50.880 --> 00:25:51.799
I just dreamt that

00:25:53.279 --> 00:25:56.279
Takeki, Miss Ye, and I...

00:25:56.759 --> 00:25:58.799
we were surrounded by the Japanese.

00:26:01.279 --> 00:26:02.160
It's okay.

00:26:02.400 --> 00:26:03.920
The two of them will be here soon.

00:26:04.119 --> 00:26:05.240
Let's take your medicine first.

00:26:05.240 --> 00:26:06.240
Okay.

00:26:13.839 --> 00:26:15.240
I've been in the hospital for a few days.

00:26:16.039 --> 00:26:17.920
I wonder how old Mr. Ye and his family

00:26:18.680 --> 00:26:20.200
have been doing lately.

00:26:21.000 --> 00:26:22.240
If you have the chance,

00:26:22.680 --> 00:26:24.319
please thank them for me.

00:26:24.319 --> 00:26:25.279
Will you?

00:26:36.079 --> 00:26:37.359
Nurse Tang

00:26:39.079 --> 00:26:40.000
What is it?

00:26:41.200 --> 00:26:41.920
It's nothing.

00:26:43.319 --> 00:26:44.039
Of course.

00:26:45.000 --> 00:26:46.799
I am also very grateful for your care.

00:26:47.400 --> 00:26:49.359
I pray to God every day,

00:26:49.359 --> 00:26:51.480
hoping the war will end soon,

00:26:51.880 --> 00:26:52.920
so that you can all live

00:26:52.920 --> 00:26:54.759
a happy and joyful life.

00:26:58.559 --> 00:27:00.799
I used to think I could be happy.

00:27:02.599 --> 00:27:03.960
Now it's impossible.

00:27:04.680 --> 00:27:05.920
What's wrong?

00:27:21.200 --> 00:27:22.200
Ah!

00:28:07.960 --> 00:28:10.039
Put your hands where I can see them.

00:28:10.880 --> 00:28:11.599
Quick!

00:28:34.839 --> 00:28:35.960
I say,

00:28:36.279 --> 00:28:37.720
it's really strange.

00:28:38.480 --> 00:28:39.759
Our police brigade

00:28:39.839 --> 00:28:41.480
searched the whole island several times,

00:28:41.480 --> 00:28:43.240
but just couldn't find you.

00:28:44.559 --> 00:28:47.359
I didn't expect you'd actually run

00:28:47.359 --> 00:28:50.039
into our hospital to recuperate.

00:28:51.079 --> 00:28:53.160
You really know how to pick a place.

00:28:55.160 --> 00:28:55.960
My dear,

00:28:57.039 --> 00:28:58.559
you just said,

00:28:58.759 --> 00:29:00.480
who is coming over in a bit?

00:29:02.960 --> 00:29:03.839
It doesn't matter.

00:29:04.839 --> 00:29:06.319
Let's wait together.

00:29:06.599 --> 00:29:07.400
My dear,

00:29:08.599 --> 00:29:09.240
go,

00:29:10.519 --> 00:29:11.680
close the curtains.

00:29:12.839 --> 00:29:14.240
Don't let people outside

00:29:14.240 --> 00:29:15.640
see what's happening inside.

00:29:16.160 --> 00:29:16.839
Go.

00:29:34.759 --> 00:29:35.759
Good girl.

00:29:36.559 --> 00:29:37.359
Come here.

00:29:44.480 --> 00:29:45.160
My dear,

00:29:46.240 --> 00:29:48.000
you've finally fallen into my hands.

00:29:49.079 --> 00:29:51.359
I won't let you go this time.

00:29:51.480 --> 00:29:52.359
Don't hurt her.

00:29:53.319 --> 00:29:54.279
Shut up.

00:29:54.759 --> 00:29:56.480
It's not up to you.

00:29:57.240 --> 00:29:58.039
Watch out.

00:29:59.200 --> 00:30:01.720
If either of you dares make a sound,

00:30:02.079 --> 00:30:03.480
I'll shoot immediately.

00:30:04.480 --> 00:30:06.079
And turn her pretty face

00:30:06.359 --> 00:30:07.920
into a bloody hole.

00:30:12.160 --> 00:30:12.960
Alright.

00:30:14.039 --> 00:30:17.039
Now let's act just like normal.

00:30:19.119 --> 00:30:20.480
Put it down.

00:30:21.480 --> 00:30:23.480
Keep quiet.

00:30:24.839 --> 00:30:26.559
Shh.

00:32:16.240 --> 00:32:17.920
Seeing the Colonel

00:32:18.400 --> 00:32:20.480
is really such a joy.

00:32:23.640 --> 00:32:26.000
Put the knife over there.

00:32:40.000 --> 00:32:40.880
Vice-Captain Inoue

00:32:41.559 --> 00:32:43.519
We can talk this over calmly

00:32:45.119 --> 00:32:46.519
What is there to talk about?

00:32:47.519 --> 00:32:49.359
You piece of Imperial Palace shit

00:32:55.519 --> 00:32:57.039
I really hate people like you

00:32:57.039 --> 00:32:58.680
who cause me trouble

00:32:59.640 --> 00:33:02.240
I should exterminate all of you

00:33:03.799 --> 00:33:04.480
Hey, beautiful

00:33:06.880 --> 00:33:08.640
Throw your bag over here

00:33:12.079 --> 00:33:13.079
Give it to him

00:33:21.319 --> 00:33:22.279
No weapons left, right?

00:33:22.480 --> 00:33:23.960
No weapons, no weapons

00:33:29.200 --> 00:33:34.839
The truth is finally out

00:33:35.279 --> 00:33:38.680
All our problems are solved

00:33:45.920 --> 00:33:47.200
Colonel

00:33:48.160 --> 00:33:50.279
How did you manage to get such a pretty lady

00:33:50.279 --> 00:33:51.599
into your hands?

00:33:53.720 --> 00:33:54.400
No wonder

00:33:55.039 --> 00:33:56.799
our Captain kept suspecting

00:33:56.799 --> 00:33:59.039
that there was something wrong here

00:34:02.480 --> 00:34:03.480
Tang Ju'er

00:34:05.480 --> 00:34:06.519
Rest assured

00:34:06.880 --> 00:34:08.920
I'll send you to the comfort station soon

00:34:10.280 --> 00:34:11.400
to keep company with that

00:34:11.400 --> 00:34:13.840
little sister named Huihui

00:34:14.639 --> 00:34:15.760
Or

00:34:16.119 --> 00:34:18.599
we can all three play together later

00:34:18.679 --> 00:34:19.400
Jerk

00:34:20.679 --> 00:34:21.360
That's right

00:34:22.159 --> 00:34:23.280
You're not wrong

00:34:26.280 --> 00:34:27.199
Hands up

00:34:29.239 --> 00:34:29.840
Quick

00:34:30.559 --> 00:34:31.519
Put your hands up

00:34:31.800 --> 00:34:32.679
Raise them

00:34:32.920 --> 00:34:33.960
You raise them too

00:34:33.960 --> 00:34:34.760
Don't sleep

00:34:39.239 --> 00:34:39.920
Right

00:34:40.960 --> 00:34:42.039
One more thing

00:34:43.960 --> 00:34:46.480
You all recognize this thing, right?

00:34:47.840 --> 00:34:49.239
Who can tell me

00:34:49.599 --> 00:34:50.840
what this is used for?

00:34:58.159 --> 00:34:59.639
What is this?

00:35:01.559 --> 00:35:02.679
Bang

00:35:08.199 --> 00:35:09.480
Look at your reactions

00:35:10.199 --> 00:35:11.480
Of course I know

00:35:11.480 --> 00:35:13.400
what this is used for

00:35:14.239 --> 00:35:15.639
You won't talk now, huh?

00:35:16.079 --> 00:35:17.039
It doesn't matter

00:35:17.760 --> 00:35:19.480
Wait until we get back to the Police Brigade

00:35:19.480 --> 00:35:20.760
We can talk slowly then

00:35:24.000 --> 00:35:25.760
Bed eight is almost fully recovered

00:35:25.760 --> 00:35:27.679
Bed two still needs observation

00:35:27.960 --> 00:35:29.199
So the rounds are done for today

00:35:29.199 --> 00:35:30.360
Yes

00:35:34.800 --> 00:35:35.719
Xiaojin

00:36:05.239 --> 00:36:05.880
Who is it?

00:36:12.679 --> 00:36:13.880
Did someone call me?

00:36:15.880 --> 00:36:16.639
Nurse Tang

00:36:17.280 --> 00:36:18.480
What is it?

00:36:20.760 --> 00:36:21.480
Nurse Tang

00:36:21.880 --> 00:36:22.719
What is it?

00:36:24.039 --> 00:36:24.800
Nurse Tang

00:36:26.280 --> 00:36:27.239
Nurse Tang

00:36:32.480 --> 00:36:33.199
Nurse Tang

00:36:36.920 --> 00:36:37.880
It's nothing

00:36:38.679 --> 00:36:40.760
Just now when I was changing his dressing

00:36:40.760 --> 00:36:42.119
I hurt him

00:36:44.480 --> 00:36:45.480
Be more careful then

00:37:02.320 --> 00:37:02.880
Ju'er

00:37:03.559 --> 00:37:04.239
Ju'er

00:37:04.960 --> 00:37:05.960
It's okay, it's okay

00:37:09.000 --> 00:37:09.840
Calm down

00:37:14.639 --> 00:37:16.000
What do we do now?

00:37:26.119 --> 00:37:26.960
It's okay

00:37:28.119 --> 00:37:29.119
It's fine

00:37:30.159 --> 00:37:31.320
It's fine

00:37:50.239 --> 00:37:54.280
Cabbages for sale, come and buy!

00:38:00.920 --> 00:38:01.920
Sir, we've arrived

00:38:03.840 --> 00:38:05.079
Alright, take care, sir

00:38:08.360 --> 00:38:09.840
Although he was my classmate

00:38:10.239 --> 00:38:11.519
he's managed to become a Colonel now

00:38:11.920 --> 00:38:14.239
I'm not as successful as him

00:38:34.639 --> 00:38:36.800
It's been a long time, Oshima-kun.

00:38:37.320 --> 00:38:39.679
You are truly a rare guest.

00:38:39.960 --> 00:38:41.239
What is it?

00:38:46.239 --> 00:38:49.840
Second Lieutenant Yamaguchi Kyuji is from Saga.

00:38:50.599 --> 00:38:51.480
Originally assigned to the 23rd Army in Hong Kong, China,

00:38:51.480 --> 00:38:52.400
from the Special Police Unit.

00:38:52.400 --> 00:38:53.760
A Second Lieutenant officer.

00:38:53.760 --> 00:38:59.079
I transferred him here; he can be trusted.

00:39:03.719 --> 00:39:04.400
Hello.

00:39:04.639 --> 00:39:05.559
It is an honor.

00:39:08.079 --> 00:39:09.639
This is my subordinate, Sasaki.

00:39:10.280 --> 00:39:11.519
Pleased to meet you.

00:39:12.280 --> 00:39:12.880
Hello.

00:39:16.239 --> 00:39:18.920
What has stumped you, Oshima-kun?

00:39:18.920 --> 00:39:20.719
From the Palace's Board of Chamberlains,

00:39:20.719 --> 00:39:22.119
a Colonel investigator has been sent.

00:39:23.719 --> 00:39:25.679
His name is Takeki Ichiro.

00:39:26.719 --> 00:39:27.320
He is responsible for investigating

00:39:27.320 --> 00:39:29.280
the crash of Admiral Osumi Mineo's plane last year.

00:39:30.360 --> 00:39:31.880
He is from the Imperial Guard Division.

00:39:33.400 --> 00:39:34.639
Then you should just cooperate.

00:39:34.639 --> 00:39:35.639
Is there a problem?

00:39:37.159 --> 00:39:39.920
Could it be that Admiral Osumi's crash

00:39:39.920 --> 00:39:41.559
has some connection to you, Oshima-kun?

00:39:41.559 --> 00:39:44.039
That is not the case.

00:39:44.519 --> 00:39:45.320
It is just that...

00:39:45.800 --> 00:39:47.559
this man has many suspicious points,

00:39:48.400 --> 00:39:51.320
yet he cannot be verified or investigated.

00:39:52.159 --> 00:39:54.760
Is there anything that cannot be investigated?

00:39:55.320 --> 00:39:57.159
This man is a special envoy of the Emperor.

00:39:57.639 --> 00:39:58.480
On his documents,

00:39:58.480 --> 00:40:00.000
there is the handwritten signature of His Majesty.

00:40:00.599 --> 00:40:01.719
Let alone me,

00:40:01.719 --> 00:40:03.480
a Captain of the Special Police Battalion,

00:40:04.239 --> 00:40:06.119
even Commander Fujita

00:40:07.639 --> 00:40:09.039
is somewhat afraid of him.

00:40:09.719 --> 00:40:10.760
Then have you verified

00:40:10.760 --> 00:40:12.280
the authenticity of that document?

00:40:13.199 --> 00:40:14.760
How can I verify it?

00:40:16.280 --> 00:40:17.920
If we only have telegrams,

00:40:17.920 --> 00:40:20.199
we have no way to verify his identity.

00:40:21.280 --> 00:40:23.119
The only way is

00:40:23.559 --> 00:40:26.599
to send a telegram to those around him,

00:40:26.599 --> 00:40:29.039
or to His Majesty himself.

00:40:29.719 --> 00:40:32.800
That is indeed somewhat troublesome.

00:40:35.800 --> 00:40:36.360
Sir,

00:40:36.480 --> 00:40:37.840
dinner is ready.

00:40:39.239 --> 00:40:40.039
Let's eat first.

00:40:40.159 --> 00:40:42.159
We can talk while we eat.

00:40:43.679 --> 00:40:44.480
That sounds good.

00:40:44.880 --> 00:40:45.559
Let's have dinner first.

00:40:47.400 --> 00:40:48.280
This way, please.

00:41:22.760 --> 00:41:23.480
That's enough.

00:41:25.000 --> 00:41:25.760
Come, please.

00:41:25.760 --> 00:41:26.280
Thank you.

00:41:26.280 --> 00:41:27.000
Don't mention it.

00:41:30.119 --> 00:41:31.119
Let me fill your cup.

00:41:33.920 --> 00:41:36.119
How many years has it been since we met?

00:41:40.000 --> 00:41:40.679
A toast to you.

00:41:40.679 --> 00:41:41.480
Cheers.

00:41:42.559 --> 00:41:43.159
I am honored.

00:41:51.199 --> 00:41:52.400
Come, let's eat.

00:41:52.719 --> 00:41:53.719
Okay.

00:41:54.639 --> 00:41:55.480
Please.

00:41:55.639 --> 00:41:56.480
Have some food.

00:41:57.880 --> 00:41:58.639
Make yourself at home.

00:41:58.639 --> 00:41:59.639
All right.

00:42:02.079 --> 00:42:03.079
I want to know,

00:42:03.559 --> 00:42:05.079
regarding the former Prime Minister Konoe Fumimaro,

00:42:05.079 --> 00:42:05.880
in the homeland and China,

00:42:05.880 --> 00:42:07.920
how many intelligence agencies has he established?

00:42:08.159 --> 00:42:09.840
Why do you ask this?

00:42:10.760 --> 00:42:12.559
The only thing I can be sure of right now

00:42:12.960 --> 00:42:13.800
is that this Colonel Takeki

00:42:13.800 --> 00:42:17.880
is a graduate of the Shanghai Tung Wen College.

00:42:17.880 --> 00:42:22.760
He should be a disciple of former Prime Minister Konoe.

00:42:23.159 --> 00:42:24.159
Is that so?

00:42:25.519 --> 00:42:26.840
Prime Minister Konoe's investigation agencies

00:42:26.840 --> 00:42:29.320
all belong to the Cabinet Intelligence Bureau.